OL,3,CWest Belfast man in court accused of
OL,4,C5G masts arson
OL,6,FA West Belfast man has been remanded
OL,7,Finto custody accused of setting fire
OL,8,Fto two 5G masts on the same night.
OL,10,FStanding in the dock of Belfast
OL,11,FMagistrates Court, 45-year-old Michael
OL,12,FClarke confirmed his identity and that
OL,13,Fhe understood the two charges against
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FClarke, from the Monagh Road in the
OL,17,Fwest of the city, is charged with two
OL,18,Fcounts of arson of 5G masts, both
OL,19,Falleged to have been committed on 1
OL,20,FJune 2023 at the Park Centre and the
OL,21,FOwenvarragh area.
