OL,3,CWest Belfast man in court accused of
OL,4,C5G masts arson
OL,6,FIn court, defence counsel Turlough
OL,7,FMadden said there was a challenge to
OL,8,Fthe police contention they had
OL,9,Fevidence to formally connect Michael
OL,10,FClarke to his charges.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Kirkpatrick told
OL,13,Fthe court that according to police
OL,14,Fcase, two men are captured on CCTV
OL,15,Fapproaching the 5G mast at Owenvarragh
OL,16,Fwith one carrying a JD Sports bag.
OL,18,FAs flames erupt from the mast the men
OL,19,Frun away, leaving the bag behind and
OL,20,Fthat was seized to be forensically
OL,21,Fexamined.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
