OL,4,C5G masts arson
OL,6,FAround an hour and a half later, two
OL,7,Findividuals wearing the same clothing
OL,8,Fare captured on CCTV approaching the
OL,9,F5G mast at the Park Centre and they
OL,10,Fuse the same modus operandi of prising
OL,11,Fopen the service hatch, pouring in an
OL,12,Faccelerant and then setting the mast
OL,13,Falight.
OL,15,FForensic examination of the JD Sports
OL,16,Fbag uncovered mixed profile DNA from
OL,17,Fthree males but when that was sent for
OL,18,Fmore extensive tests, the DNA profile
OL,19,Fof Michael Clarke was found on it.
