OL,4,C5G masts arson
OL,6,FWhen his home was searched earlier
OL,7,Fthis week, investigators seized petrol
OL,8,Fcans, a key used to open mast service
OL,9,Fhatches, literature concerning the
OL,10,Falleged dangers posed by 5G masts as
OL,11,Fwell as legal guidelines on the crime
OL,12,Fof criminal damage and possible
OL,13,Fdefences to it.
