OL,6,FDC Kirkpatrick told the court that
OL,7,Fwhen Clarke was interviewed, "he said
OL,8,Fthat he was a freeman of the land" and
OL,9,Falthough he refused to answer
OL,10,Fquestions about the actual incident,
OL,11,F"he went on a bit of a rant that we
OL,12,Fwill all be un-alived unless we wake
OL,13,Fup."
OL,15,FDuring cross-examination, the officer
OL,16,Fagreed with Mr Madden that the bag "is
OL,17,Fa movable object," that two other
OL,18,Fprofiles of unknown males had been
OL,19,Ffound on it and that more than two
OL,20,Fyears had passed between the incident
OL,21,Fand Clarke's arrest.
