OL,6,FHe also agreed that "it's not a crime"
OL,7,Fto have the literature which was found
OL,8,Fin Clarke's home and also that
OL,9,Fclothing worn by the arsonists on the
OL,10,FCCTV had not been found in the
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FDC Kirkpatrick acknowledged also that
OL,14,Fno one has looked at the footage and
OL,15,Fbeen able to identify Clarke as an
OL,16,Falleged culprit.
