OL,4,C5G masts arson
OL,6,FSubmitting there was insufficient
OL,7,Fevidence to establish a formal
OL,8,Fconnection, Mr Madden highlighted that
OL,9,F"it's a high, highly circumstantial
OL,10,Fcase" and one which had "multiple
OL,11,Ftriable issues."
OL,13,F"The police are asking the court to
OL,14,Fjump over a significant circumstantial
OL,15,Fhurdle here to connect the accused,"
OL,16,Fthe barrister suggested.
