OL,6,FDistrict Judge Natasha Fitzsimmons
OL,7,Fsaid however, given the "low bar" for
OL,8,Fconnection, she was satisfied, given
OL,9,Fthe forensic and circumstantial
OL,10,Fevidence, "I consider that I can
OL,11,Fconnect him."
OL,13,FBail was refused and Clarke was
OL,14,Fremanded into custody, she adjourned
OL,15,Fthe case to 19 September.
